checkersMain
Class CheckersPlayerLoader

java.lang.Object
  checkersMain.CheckersPlayerLoader

public final class CheckersPlayerLoader
extends java.lang.Object

A final class that is not instantiable. It provides static methods to load the CheckersPlayerInterfaces in the checkersPlayer package and retrieve their classes and display names.

Version:
1.00 - 25 July 2008
Author:
Amos Yuen
